f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:18:26.000Z","msg":"根據份annual financial statement<br />\nTVB其實一直每年都蝕緊錢<br />\n背後有大金主 而金主本身有冇貪污同洗錢就冇人知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:42:29.000Z","msg":"push比多d人知<br />\n大金主快d拎多錢出黎救tvb啦<br />\n<br />\n但點救都無用 死法同atv一樣<br />\n<br />\n係分早dd 定遲dd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0513d7eacd06b2f019b7a0751bafc1e52397291d","tid":1234831,"uid":24339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:44:18.000Z","msg":"仆你個街，無綫嚟嘅喂"},{"pid":"8aff1d7a32283c6bc1cd3f5654687c370256ce86","tid":1234831,"uid":157938,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:55:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>繼續推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n<br />\nTVB在反送中報導一事，已經嚴重違反電視通用業務守則中有關「第9章準確、持平及公正」，當中要求「持牌人必須盡一切合理努力，確保新聞、時事節目...的真實資料準確無誤」，以及「持牌人必須確保新聞節目...能夠恰當地持平」，「不可使用謬誤資料或歪曲事實。持牌人亦不應錯誤引導觀眾，以致對節目提及的人士或團體不公平」<br />\n<br />\nTVB在反送中的報導完全扭曲事相，報導嚴重偏袒警方和政府，報導失實 ， 偏頗，例如6月12日的「六點半新聞報道」和「晚間新聞」，完全不播放及不提及：<br />\n1. 警方違法向多名記者開槍，棍打記者<br />\n2. 警方違法瞄準市民頭部發射布袋彈和橡膠子彈<br />\n3. 在沒有任何襲擊下，警方違法向婦孺、伯伯開槍<br />\n4. 警方違法向市民投擲鐵枝、磗頭<br />\n5. 隻字不提一些市民向警方掟水樽垃圾等之前，警方在多處在沒有受到任何襲擊，提出任何警告下，違法突然向市民開槍，不斷發射催淚彈，布袋彈和橡膠子彈，導致局勢快速失控<br />\n6.隻字不提有市民於6月15日於太古廣場因展示示威標語墮樓, 送院搶救後不治的事實<br />\n<br />\n投訴表格：<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=4IeBTxJtadAFWj01jWWaWk6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=d8289a6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日期： 2019/6/12 時間1830 新聞報導</span></span>"},{"pid":"e6019a6ab324fac5e5b51536275a17ce7c5c2120","tid":1234831,"uid":260653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:04:18.000Z","msg":"我地有責任同係tvb落廣告既公司講 我唔睇tvb架！ <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1237523\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1237523</a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"30b5dc74b9f07aae0de193e77278e5a2b57ab54a","tid":1234831,"uid":77416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:07:45.000Z","msg":"PUSH!!<br />\n之前成日幫手推TVB D 膠劇<br />\n我係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"469f356a5702ee33654402caf790344911e3a345","tid":1234831,"uid":137166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T22:06:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0fb9ccee166ae5d34462555cd5c154c872ed61c2","tid":1234831,"uid":192754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T22:07:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}